---
// Deep Memory Research Agent — 6-stage retrieval pipeline
---

<div class="rp">
  <div class="rp__title-bar">
    <span class="rp__title-dot"></span>
    <span class="rp__title-text">DEEP MEMORY RESEARCH AGENT — 6-STAGE RETRIEVAL</span>
  </div>

  <div class="rp__stages">
    <div class="rp__stage" data-stage="1">
      <div class="rp__num">01</div>
      <div class="rp__body">
        <h4 class="rp__name">Query Interpretation</h4>
        <p class="rp__desc">Decompose question into retrieval targets: topic entities, domains, constraints, time periods, authority needs.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rp__wire"></div>

    <div class="rp__stage" data-stage="2">
      <div class="rp__num">02</div>
      <div class="rp__body">
        <h4 class="rp__name">Broad Candidate Harvest</h4>
        <p class="rp__desc">FTS5 search + temporal filtering across memory objects. Optimize for recall — miss nothing material.</p>
        <div class="rp__tool">
          <span class="rp__tool-badge">MCP</span>
          <code>search_memory_candidates</code>
          <code>temporal_query</code>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rp__wire"></div>

    <div class="rp__stage" data-stage="3">
      <div class="rp__num">03</div>
      <div class="rp__body">
        <h4 class="rp__name">Evidence Triage</h4>
        <p class="rp__desc">Score candidates across 6 composite dimensions. Not just semantic similarity — authority, temporal validity, causal relevance, and contradiction signal.</p>
        <div class="rp__scores">
          <div class="rp__score-row">
            <span class="rp__score-label">Semantic</span>
            <div class="rp__score-bar"><div class="rp__score-fill" style="width: 20%"></div></div>
            <span class="rp__score-wt">0.20</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rp__score-row">
            <span class="rp__score-label">Constraint</span>
            <div class="rp__score-bar"><div class="rp__score-fill rp__score-fill--warn" style="width: 25%"></div></div>
            <span class="rp__score-wt">0.25</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rp__score-row">
            <span class="rp__score-label">Authority</span>
            <div class="rp__score-bar"><div class="rp__score-fill" style="width: 20%"></div></div>
            <span class="rp__score-wt">0.20</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rp__score-row">
            <span class="rp__score-label">Temporal</span>
            <div class="rp__score-bar"><div class="rp__score-fill rp__score-fill--dim" style="width: 15%"></div></div>
            <span class="rp__score-wt">0.15</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rp__score-row">
            <span class="rp__score-label">Causal</span>
            <div class="rp__score-bar"><div class="rp__score-fill rp__score-fill--dim" style="width: 10%"></div></div>
            <span class="rp__score-wt">0.10</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rp__score-row">
            <span class="rp__score-label">Contradiction</span>
            <div class="rp__score-bar"><div class="rp__score-fill rp__score-fill--red" style="width: 10%"></div></div>
            <span class="rp__score-wt">0.10</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rp__wire"></div>

    <div class="rp__stage" data-stage="4">
      <div class="rp__num">04</div>
      <div class="rp__body">
        <h4 class="rp__name">Drill-down Expansion</h4>
        <p class="rp__desc">For high-value candidates: traverse memory graph to rebuild full reasoning chains. Follow supports, derived_from, depends_on edges up to 3 hops.</p>
        <div class="rp__tool">
          <span class="rp__tool-badge">MCP</span>
          <code>expand_memory_neighbors</code>
          <code>load_evidence_span</code>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rp__wire"></div>

    <div class="rp__stage rp__stage--warn" data-stage="5">
      <div class="rp__num rp__num--warn">05</div>
      <div class="rp__body">
        <h4 class="rp__name">Conflict &amp; Supersession</h4>
        <p class="rp__desc">Walk supersession chains. Detect contradictions. Determine current governing position. Never cite a stale decision without noting its replacement.</p>
        <div class="rp__tool">
          <span class="rp__tool-badge rp__tool-badge--warn">MCP</span>
          <code>get_supersession_chain</code>
          <code>get_conflict_set</code>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rp__wire"></div>

    <div class="rp__stage rp__stage--output" data-stage="6">
      <div class="rp__num rp__num--green">06</div>
      <div class="rp__body">
        <h4 class="rp__name">Context Packet Synthesis</h4>
        <p class="rp__desc">Assemble structured ContextPacket: material memories, binding constraints, contradictions, evidence lineage, coverage assessment. No text blobs — structured JSON for downstream agents.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .rp {
    margin: var(--space-2xl) 0;
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .rp__title-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .rp__title-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #A78BFA;
  }

  .rp__title-text {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .rp__stages {
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .rp__stage {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .rp__stage--warn { border-color: rgba(255, 184, 0, 0.3); }
  .rp__stage--output {
    border-color: rgba(0, 255, 178, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(0, 255, 178, 0.08);
  }

  .rp__num {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: 4px;
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .rp__num > * { transform: rotate(-45deg); }
  .rp__num--warn { color: var(--color-warning); border-color: var(--color-warning); }
  .rp__num--green { color: var(--color-accent); border-color: var(--color-accent); }

  .rp__body { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }

  .rp__name {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .rp__desc {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .rp__wire {
    width: 1px;
    height: 20px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    opacity: 0.25;
    margin: 0 0 0 14px;
  }

  /* MCP tool badges */
  .rp__tool {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .rp__tool-badge {
    font-size: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 1px 5px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    color: #A78BFA;
    background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.25);
  }

  .rp__tool-badge--warn {
    color: var(--color-warning);
    background: rgba(255, 184, 0, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(255, 184, 0, 0.25);
  }

  .rp__tool code {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    padding: 1px 5px;
  }

  /* Score bars */
  .rp__scores { margin-top: var(--space-sm); }

  .rp__score-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: 2px 0;
  }

  .rp__score-label {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    min-width: 80px;
  }

  .rp__score-bar {
    flex: 1;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .rp__score-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .rp__score-fill--warn { background: var(--color-warning); }
  .rp__score-fill--dim { background: var(--color-text-muted); opacity: 0.5; }
  .rp__score-fill--red { background: var(--color-error); }

  .rp__score-wt {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    min-width: 24px;
    text-align: right;
  }
</style>
